# The analyzer DEFAULTS to the TRANSFORMER model en_core_web_trf — required to
# meet the per-type recall targets (it lifts PERSON/DATE/PHONE to ~1.0). It pulls
# torch and is large/slower on CPU; en_core_web_lg is the faster, lower-recall
# alternative (AnalyzerConfig(spacy_model="en_core_web_lg")). Models aren't on
# PyPI; install with:
#
#     python -m spacy download en_core_web_trf      # default
#     python -m spacy download en_core_web_lg       # fast alternative
#
# For a pinned / offline install (threat T8 — mirror the artifact inside the
# trust boundary), add the release wheel here, aligned to the resolved spaCy
# version, e.g.:
#
#     en_core_web_trf @ https://github.com/explosion/spacy-models/releases/download/en_core_web_trf-3.8.0/en_core_web_trf-3.8.0-py3-none-any.whl

